                        <handDesc hands="1">
                            <handNote scribe="JonArn005" scope="sole" script="unknown">
                                <p>According to Jón Ólafsson's catalogue (<ref target="#AM02-0384-en">AM 384 fol</ref>) the manuscript is
                                    written by <name type="person" key="JonArn005">Jón
                                        Arnórsson</name>..</p>
